ncrease in the already existing 2-hand Damage muliplier. The only way to see this bonus for 2-hand weapons based on the Damage then would be to parse the data with a 1-hander and a 2-hander with the same stats (well Damage wise anyways) <p>Kahm FierceHeart, Tunare luvin Paladin of 54 Seasons <br>
